From 56c0290202ab94a2f2780c449395d4ae8495fab4 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Christophe JAILLET <christophe.jaillet@wanadoo.fr>
Date: Sat, 6 Jan 2018 09:00:09 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] mdio-sun4i: Fix a memory leak
Git-commit: 56c0290202ab94a2f2780c449395d4ae8495fab4
Patch-mainline: v4.15-rc8
References: bsc#1051510

If the probing of the regulator is deferred, the memory allocated by
'mdiobus_alloc_size()' will be leaking.
It should be freed before the next call to 'sun4i_mdio_probe()' which will
reallocate it.

Fixes: 4bdcb1dd9feb ("net: Add MDIO bus driver for the Allwinner EMAC")
Signed-off-by: Christophe JAILLET <christophe.jaillet@wanadoo.fr>
Signed-off-by: David S. Miller <davem@davemloft.net>
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

---
